HON. VICENTE GONZALEZ

                                of texas

                    in the house of representatives

                      Wednesday, November 1, 2017
content.speaker: None

content.text:
Mr. GONZALEZ of Texas. Mr. Speaker, I was unable to cast my vote on 
October 31, 2017 for Roll Call Vote 591. Had I been present, my vote 
would have been the following: Aye on Roll Call Vote 591
content.speaker: Mr. GONZALEZ of Texas
